OL,3,CHottest January on record shatters
OL,4,Cglobal temperatures
OL,6,FBut last month was 0.79C above the
OL,7,F1991-2020 global average for the month
OL,8,Fand 1.75C above pre-industrial levels,
OL,9,Fscientists from the EU's Copernicus
OL,10,FClimate Change Service (C3S) said,
OL,11,Fbreaking January 2024's record by
OL,12,Fnearly 0.1C.
OL,14,FIt is the 18th month in the last 19
OL,15,Fwhere average global air surface
OL,16,Ftemperatures were more than 1.5C above
OL,17,Fthe 1850-1900 level.
