OL,3,CHottest January on record shatters
OL,4,Cglobal temperatures
OL,6,FOutside Europe, temperatures were most
OL,7,Fabove average over parts of Canada,
OL,8,FAlaska, and Siberia. They were also
OL,9,Fabove average over southern South
OL,10,FAmerica, Africa, and much of Australia
OL,11,Fand Antarctica.
OL,13,FTemperatures were most notably below
OL,14,Faverage over the US and the
OL,15,Feasternmost regions of Russia. The
OL,16,FArabian Peninsula and Southeast Asia
OL,17,Falso had below-average temperatures.
